divs: Sighting DetailsDaylight sighting,I was outside feeding my cat when I looked up,because it felt like someone was watching me, disc shape object appeared in sky, no noise and bronze in color moved slowy across the sky, and then went straight up and out of sight.I didn't know what to think of it,so I asked my neighbor. She told me to report the sighting to the mufon.I still can't believe that I saw it.
